Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs22\shad1\c&H70D8FB&\fn迷你简汉真广标\b0\pos(308,397)\fsp1}漫迪字幕组倾情奉献{\fsp0}\N\N——·@孙悟空&旗木译制·——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 Daria 我今天没看见你\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, Daria. I didn't see you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过要来摄影大会讨论年鉴的事来着\N{\fnArial\fs18}You said you might come to the photography meeting for yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀 可等牙医关掉话匣子时\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, well, when the dentist turned off the gas,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我就改变了心意\N{\fnArial\fs18}I had a change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但这很有趣的 而且对你成绩也有好处\N{\fnArial\fs18}But it's fun, and it looks good on your transcript.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我对这两件事都有抵触\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm against both those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,自由摄影和冲印呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Free film and developing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你父母发现你在考虑这件事\N{\fnArial\fs18}And if your parents find out that you're even considering it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你还很有可能搞到一笔可观的贿赂\N{\fnArial\fs18}you could probably squeeze some tremendous bribe out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我再考虑考虑\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信你们竟然想贿赂我... 拿毛票儿\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't believe you're trying to bribe me... with singles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,甜心 这不是贿赂 这是约定\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sweetie, it's not a bribe, it's a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说 你比我的客户还糟糕\N{\fnArial\fs18}Honestly, you're worse than my clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.68,0:01:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,年鉴完全扭曲了真实的高中生活\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yearbooks completely distort the reality of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了 年鉴经历能为个人网站提供素材\N{\fnArial\fs18}Of course, the yearbook experience could provide material for a web page...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有软件就好了\N{\fnArial\fs18}if I had the software.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那就买软件吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Software it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,约美男 不能聊咯 再见\N{\fnArial\fs18}Big date! Can't talk! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你是Daria对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey! You're Daria, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Ted 图片编辑\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm Ted, the photo editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过你的照片\N{\fnArial\fs18}I saw your pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,废话不多说 直接解雇我吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then cut the small talk and get straight to firing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好笑 因为你说的和我要说的完全相反 了解?\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's funny, because it's the exact opposite of the truth, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你在玩黑色幽默吧 对吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're using sarcasm, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 我刚才说得蛮认真的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Actually, I was being sincere for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪个星球来的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What planet are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,星球? 嘿 又用了夸张 很有意思嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Planet? Hey! Hyperbole! Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但说真的 我很喜欢你的照片\N{\fnArial\fs18}But, seriously, though, I loved your photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你的作品看起来有种西班牙风格\N{\fnArial\fs18}Your composition seems very Spanish,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,和弗朗西斯科·戈雅的农民画没什么不同\N{\fnArial\fs18}not unlike the peasant paintings of Francisco Goya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}西班牙浪漫主义画家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是戈雅的头号粉丝 你呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm a huge Goya fanatic. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯... 是 头号粉\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um... yeah, huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,戈雅的描绘主题多为死亡 毁灭 残忍\N{\fnArial\fs18}Actually, Goya liked to paint death, destruction, brutality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该交点有学问的笔友\N{\fnArial\fs18}You'd have made good pen pals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}戈雅作品集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思的是 他从不去学校上课\N{\fnArial\fs18}And the interesting part is, he's never been to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,直到现在都是他父母在家里教他\N{\fnArial\fs18}His parents have taught him at home until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这难道不酷吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Isn't that kind of cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我向来根据结果断事 所以我得说... 不酷\N{\fnArial\fs18}I judge things by results, so I would have to say... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 黑色幽默 你俩肯定有得聊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, sarcasm. You two would get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他让你入邪教了 网页软件能让给我吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}If he makes you join his cult, can I have your web page software?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在什么邪教\N{\fnArial\fs18}He doesn't belong to a cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那个包装看起来也不像什么软件\N{\fnArial\fs18}And the shrink-wrap never comes off that software.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真能拿到的话 我会立马去换成杀人游戏盘\N{\fnArial\fs18}Soon as I get it, I'm exchanging it for Cannibal Fragfest on CD-ROM.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,电脑极端暴力\N{\fnArial\fs18}Computer ultra-violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,戈雅肯定会喜欢的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Goya would have loved that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 既然你问了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, since you ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我有在尝试营造出明暗的高度对比\N{\fnArial\fs18}I was kind of trying to get a high contrast of light and dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}奥古斯都时期第三个重要诗人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮 你肯定读了不少奥维德的诗篇\N{\fnArial\fs18}Neat! You must read a lot of Ovid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}奥芬巴赫所作轻歌剧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我六岁时读了《地狱中的奥菲欧》现在仍然萦绕耳畔\N{\fnArial\fs18}I read Orpheus in the Underworld when I was six, and it still haunts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 是啊 我也是\N{\fnArial\fs18}Uh, yeah. Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 我得和父母谈谈让我进学校接受正规教育了\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know, I had to talk my parents into let me go to a normal school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,几号开学?\N{\fnArial\fs18}When do you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色幽默 但我喜欢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Irony! But I like it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望志愿活动或募捐活动\N{\fnArial\fs18}I only wish that volunteering or charity fundraising
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在年鉴上获得和运动队 俱乐部同样多的版面\N{\fnArial\fs18}got as much yearbook space as sports and clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,DeMartino老师?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mr. DeMartino?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria和我刚才在谈学校有些学生\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria and I were just saying that there are some students at school
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的与众不同\N{\fnArial\fs18}who are really making a difference,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我们在年鉴里对他们过于轻描淡写了\N{\fnArial\fs18}and maybe we're short-changing them a little bit in the yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真高尚啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}How noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,或许你觉得我们应该缩减运动队和俱乐部的版面\N{\fnArial\fs18}Perhaps you think we should cut some pages from sports and clubs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,为他们腾空间?\N{\fnArial\fs18}to make more room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 好主意 先生\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey! Good idea, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们暂停并深思一下 各位\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let me pause and reflect. Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,运动队和俱乐部版面缩减十页\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sports and clubs are cut by ten pages!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不能啊 - 这太不公平了\N{\fnArial\fs18}- You can't do that! - But that's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我主意\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not my idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是被自己的同类妨害的\N{\fnArial\fs18}You've been sabotaged by your own kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是他们想到的\N{\fnArial\fs18}They thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这点子会很赞的\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is going to be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 叛徒\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hello, traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对叛徒来说真是好天儿 不是吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's a nice day, isn't it... for a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我压根没信仰过的东西 何谈背叛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How can I betray something I don't believe in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,友情提示一下 运动队就好像年鉴的跳动的心...\N{\fnArial\fs18}In case you didn't know, sports are, like, the beating heart of the yearbook...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...心脏\N{\fnArial\fs18}um, system!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 而且加入法语俱乐部...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Plus, it's like getting in the yearbook is the only reason
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为的就是能上年鉴\N{\fnArial\fs18}to join French Club in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 Brittany 你对法国人和他们文化的深厚感情呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Gee, Brittany, what about your deep love for French people and their culture?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起... 年鉴危机都把人家搞凌乱了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry... this yearbook crisis is just messing me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 宝贝\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's all right babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你做什么了吗? 叛徒\N{\fnArial\fs18}See what you've done? Traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,简直是无礼\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's totally rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可恶\N{\fnArial\fs18}Completely heinous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎Daria这个女孩根本不明事理什么的\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's like this girl Daria doesn't understand reason, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说她是个书呆子\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, I hear she's a brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,跟书呆子说不上道理的\N{\fnArial\fs18}You can't reason with brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是要找她谈谈\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm still going to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,作为时尚俱乐部主席 我还是有点震慑力的\N{\fnArial\fs18}As president of the Fashion Club, I can be kind of intimidating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你绝对唬得住人 Sandi\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, you're definitely scary, Sandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我觉得这案例很特殊 我来做工作吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}But I think this is a special case, so let me talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能交给我做 我会很感激的\N{\fnArial\fs18}It would mean so much if you let me try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好了\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有 你啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不会是认真的吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}But you can't be serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 Ted说的有道理\N{\fnArial\fs18}Listen, Ted has a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因为那个男孩\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,搞半天你就是喜欢人家 对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, it's all about love, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是喜欢\N{\fnArial\fs18}It is not about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 让你那点小秘密停留在永恒里吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}All right, keep it your secret to cherish always.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但就因为你要出去约会...\N{\fnArial\fs18}But just because you're going out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ted和我没在约会\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ted and I are not going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,随便了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托告诉"心水男" 我们要夺年鉴回来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Just tell "loverboy" we want our yearbook back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这话有语病诶\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你把动词"夺"和名词"年鉴"连起来用了\N{\fnArial\fs18}You just used the verb "want" with the noun "book."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你的男朋友去玩数字游戏吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Save the math games for your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 真高兴你能过来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Gosh, I'm glad you could come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,找路没太费周折吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did you have any trouble finding it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你家前院的玉米快没过我的脑袋了\N{\fnArial\fs18}The corn growing in your front yard sort of tipped me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我家后院种的是南瓜和豆子\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah. We keep the squash and beans in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我脑袋里满满都是想要和你分享的摄影点子\N{\fnArial\fs18}I've got all these photo ideas that I want to tell you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}罗斯福从政时期的政府部门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得促进就业局那种风沙侵蚀的黑白纪录片风格最完美了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I think a WPA black-and-white dust bowl documentary style would be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 嘿 这是什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, yeah. Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸和我一起做的留声机啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, that's the phonograph my dad and I made,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,听别人口里描述的电视机 这个一点也不差\N{\fnArial\fs18}and from what I've heard about television, this is just as good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我这儿有一些古乐器演奏的早期音乐\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, I have some early music played on period instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,听了会有种你就站在古大提琴旁边的感觉\N{\fnArial\fs18}You feel like you're right there in front of the viola da gamba!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,其实Ted 还是安安静静比较好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Actually, Ted, maybe just quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,沙发居然是全木的\N{\fnArial\fs18}This couch is all wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是你和你爸做的 对不对?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You and your dad made it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,长叶松木 很绵软\N{\fnArial\fs18}Georgia pine! Very soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 够了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, that does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 Ted 我跟你不在一个轨道\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm sorry Ted; I can't keep up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不在一个轨道? 说什么啦?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Keep up? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是超群的那个\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're the remarkable one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 希望你不要误解 但你真的是个全才\N{\fnArial\fs18}I mean, please don't take this wrong, but you've got it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 给 来片口香糖吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, thanks. Here, want some gum?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我想等话全都说明白了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess when all is said and done,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:07:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会发现其实我们只是普通美国高中生\N{\fnArial\fs18}we're just a couple of ordinary American teenagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ted?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ted?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是口香糖\N{\fnArial\fs18}So this is gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢 妈 爸 口香糖 我吃口香糖了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I like it! Mom! Dad! Gum! I got gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgendorffer家嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Morgendorffers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}以环保工作为主的国际性非政府组织
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是绿色和平组织的吗? 我家来过人了\N{\fnArial\fs18}If this is for Greenpeace, uh, we've already given.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,绿色和平? 那帮蝇营狗苟的家伙?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Greenpeace? Those corporate puppets?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认识二位嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Do we know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Leslie Dewitt\N{\fnArial\fs18}Leslie Dewitt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Grant Clinton 我们是Ted Dewitt-Clinton父母\N{\fnArial\fs18}Grant Clinton. Ted Dewitt-Clinton's parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,打断下 他是不是那天和Quinn出去玩的哪个男孩?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry, is he one of the boys who went out with Quinn the other night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这个你们认得吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Does this look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,口香糖?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Gum?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 你们女儿Daria的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, from your daughter Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,二位要进来喝点什么吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Would you like to come in for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是酒吧 我猜\N{\fnArial\fs18}Alcohol, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我算知道那丫头怎么那样了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, now I see where she gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我来烧一壶咖啡\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll make a pot of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,咖啡?!\N{\fnArial\fs18}Caffeine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我搞不太懂现在问题在哪\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't really understand the problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,也难怪\N{\fnArial\fs18}Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些人...\N{\fnArial\fs18}You people are happy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,咀嚼着所谓现代社会的空虚物质就很开心了\N{\fnArial\fs18}chewing on the empty offerings of so-called modern society.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,别让它们靠近我儿子的嘴 我们就感激涕零了\N{\fnArial\fs18}We'd just appreciate it if you kept them away from our son's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,给我听好 嬉皮\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, look here, hippy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria有时确实比较棘手\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria may be a handful sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但就因为她给你儿子口香糖 也没必要平白无故...\N{\fnArial\fs18}but just because she gave your kid some gum is no reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不单是口香糖\N{\fnArial\fs18}It wasn't just the gum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她还给了他这个\N{\fnArial\fs18}She also gave him this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,披头士?\N{\fnArial\fs18}The Beatles?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们保护他大半辈子 却没人在乎\N{\fnArial\fs18}We've tried so hard, and nobody seems to care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么Ted是什么人?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who the hell is this Ted kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我们的邻居们也都怪怪的\N{\fnArial\fs18}And what's happening to our neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,最开始是种起玉米 现在又这样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}First people growing corn, now this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 他可能是有点怪 但也有点可爱啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, maybe he is a little weird, but he's also a little sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这不重要吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Isn't that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,重要不过他从没吃过口香糖这事实\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not as important as the fact that he never had gum before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好萌 你和一个怪咖纠结起来了\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is so cute! You're involved with a kook!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没在纠结\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're not involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 Daria 我找你来着\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hi, Daria! I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我雕了这条项链给你 谢谢你给我口香糖\N{\fnArial\fs18}I carved you this necklace, as thanks for the gum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好美啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜某人开始纠结了吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess somebody here is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,纠结什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Involved in what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 有人想吃鹰嘴豆泥吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, who wants some hummus?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能要这个 拿回去吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't take this. Keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但我希望你能收下\N{\fnArial\fs18}But I want you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我亲手做...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ted 我不能收下\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ted, I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是一起策划年鉴\N{\fnArial\fs18}We work together on yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不是要给对方做什么项链\N{\fnArial\fs18}We don't make jewelry for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是在玩黑色幽默或者夸张吧 有吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You aren't being sarcastic or hyperbolic, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没\N{\fnArial\fs18}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那... 我们年鉴策划会上见吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, then I guess I'll see you at yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,做对事了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 有人给我亲手做了一条项链\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah. A guy makes me a necklace by hand
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我却像收到核废料一样\N{\fnArial\fs18}and I act like it's nuclear waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我做了对的事\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sure. I did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 现在你是在黑色幽默\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, now you're being sarcastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我们之前从没听说过这个男孩?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But why haven't we heard about this boy before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他是怪咖\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because he's a freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怪胎... 挺好 对吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Freak is, uh, good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对 要是你们觉得加入邪教挺好的话\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, if you think belonging to a cult is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 那个邪教里的每个人都穿得巨丑 还隔绝社会\N{\fnArial\fs18}Plus, everybody in the cult has to wear ugly clothes and be completely unsocial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,坏到不行\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,邪教?\N{\fnArial\fs18}A cult?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ted是什么人 你怎么从没跟我们说过\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who is Ted and why haven't you told us about him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他有教唆你加入邪教吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}and is he trying to get you to join a cult?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他管自己叫老兄?\N{\fnArial\fs18}He calls himself brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,叫Ted老兄啥的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You mean like Brother Ted?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我是说 "老兄 你们疯了吧"\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, like, "Oh, brother, you're all crazy."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ted是一起做年鉴的好学生\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ted is a nice guy from yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他有点怪 但不在什么邪教\N{\fnArial\fs18}He's odd, but he's not in a cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,最后说一次 我们没有在约会\N{\fnArial\fs18}And for the last time, we are not going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她显然在撒谎 - 绝对的 - 毋庸置疑\N{\fnArial\fs18}- She's obviously lying. - Absolutely. - No question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:09:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能跟她谈谈 Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can't you talk to her, Quinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛不带着她去和你的那些朋友玩玩?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why don't you set her up with one of your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都还蛮正常的\N{\fnArial\fs18}They're all normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 所以我要是真带Daria出去 他们会笑掉大牙的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, and that's exactly why they would laugh me out of town if I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你肯 妈妈和我会给你甜头吃的\N{\fnArial\fs18}If you do, Mom and I will make it sweet for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什么甜头?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,资助你给个人主页加声效怎么样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How does your own web page sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不如给我来一双"咯噔咯噔咯噔"响...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not as nice as the crunch-crunch-crunch sound
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,能在高中停车场穿出去的新鞋好呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}of a new pair of shoes on the high school parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,成 Quinn 你最最好了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Deal! Quinn, you're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不太懂为什么要帮一个平白无故的衰人找男朋友\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't understand why we should help some random loser find a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看 这正是你们这种消极主义的人的想法\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, that's exactly the kind of negative attitude that says,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"我只是时尚新闻的旁观者 不是时尚新闻的缔造者"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"I'm a fashion news reader and not a fashion news maker."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 Sandi\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thank you, Sandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可我们找谁做她男朋友啊?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But who will we get to be her date?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Robert?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望我们能一直许你坐我们旁边这桌 对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You like being allowed to sit at the other end of our table, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 女士\N{\fnArial\fs18}Uh, yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那我可有个任务要派给你\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then I have an assignment for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 女士\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我对Ted是不是太刻薄了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Do you think I was too mean to Ted?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是什么老兄 也不在邪教里\N{\fnArial\fs18}He's not a brother, and he's not in a cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是很坦诚 很道义 很聪颖\N{\fnArial\fs18}He's just very honest and ethical and smart,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不应该那么刻薄的\N{\fnArial\fs18}and I shouldn't have been so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真心蛮在乎他的 有没有?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Whoa. You're really into him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没 但我真心喜欢因为他 我父母诚惶诚恐\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, but I do like the way he scares my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定惹毛爸妈是建立良好关系的基础?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Are you sure annoying your parents is good grounds for a relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,罗密欧和朱丽叶不就是\N{\fnArial\fs18}It was for Romeo and Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ted 我想我欠你一句对不起\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, Ted, I think I owe you an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你的项链很漂亮 我没有收下太无礼了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Your necklace was beautiful and I was a jerk for not taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真的? 很好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Really? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那我希望你能允许我请你吃披萨\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then I was hoping you'd let me buy you a slice of pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白讲 Daria 我想也许你是对的\N{\fnArial\fs18}To be honest, Daria, I think maybe you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该把友情严格限定在年鉴策划的层面\N{\fnArial\fs18}We should keep our friendship on a strictly yearbook level.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 你这是在埋怨我吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wait a minute. Are you blowing me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 我爸妈警告过我传统学校的孩子可能会有点...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, my parents warned me that kids in conventional school can be kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,肤浅\N{\fnArial\fs18}shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我肤浅?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You think I'm shallow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你有点让我想到那个常能见到的人缘很好的女孩\N{\fnArial\fs18}You sort of remind me of that really popular girl I've seen around...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好像叫Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识她吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩也许会比较处得来\N{\fnArial\fs18}You'd probably get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来《呕心小世界: 骗局还是幻影?》\N{\fnArial\fs18}Next on Sick, Sad World: hoax, or vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,佛罗里达州有人声称见到了耶稣阵容... 在硬币上\N{\fnArial\fs18}Some people in Florida claim they've seen the face of Jesus... on a penny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 如果从马上面下来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Look, when you get thrown off a horse,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你得重新站起来射杀它 对嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}you have to get back up and shoot it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,话说我认识一个萌男 对你非常迷恋哦\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, I know this cute guy who's got a huge crush on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们四人约会吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let's double!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,得了 要么你是在整侮辱我的桥段\N{\fnArial\fs18}All right, this is either a plot to humiliate me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要么就是需要我跟你出去 好帮你做点什么事\N{\fnArial\fs18}or you need me to go so I can do something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦 是把戏啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, okay, it's a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能来 爸妈会把我的宵禁时限延后半小时\N{\fnArial\fs18}If you come, Mom and Dad will extend my curfew by half an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,另外我在跟一个叨逼叨没完的叫Shawn的家伙约会\N{\fnArial\fs18}plus I'm dating this guy Shawn who never shuts up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,需要一个能说会道的人在身边\N{\fnArial\fs18}I want someone else there who can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 省省吧 - 十刀怎样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Forget it. - Ten bucks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 每小时 - 定了\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Per hour. - You're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 我变主意了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Nope, I've changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on, Daria!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让老爸老妈亲自给你张罗男朋友吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You want Mom and Dad to set you up with somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧收视准备吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, hurry up and get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想吃鞋店的闭门羹\N{\fnArial\fs18}I want to get to the shoe store before it closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那... 我们今天约会都要玩些什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, what exactly are we going to do on our date?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 别说话 Shawn\N{\fnArial\fs18}- What? - Quiet, Shawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就四处开车逛逛 转转便利店啥的 随便啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}We'll drive around; go to a convenience store... whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,随便做点年轻人爱干的事呗\N{\fnArial\fs18}The usual random teenage shenanigans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是挺好? 跟她说话呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}Isn't that great? Talk to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 你怎么看...\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, what do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,联合国下发的排放控制令对第三国家的影响?\N{\fnArial\fs18}of UN-mandated emission control laws for Third World countries?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,理念崇高 但给出的时间表不切实际\N{\fnArial\fs18}Noble idea, but the UN's time table is unrealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一样\N{\fnArial\fs18}Uh, same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,同意还是不同意:\N{\fnArial\fs18}Agree or disagree:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,利用贸易禁令对抗侵犯人权的国家非常有效\N{\fnArial\fs18}trade embargoes are an effective way to deal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,利用贸易禁令对抗侵犯人权的国家非常有效\N{\fnArial\fs18}with countries that vi-o-late human rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,同意 但面对中国这样的贸易伙伴巨头\N{\fnArial\fs18}Agreed, but with major trading partners like China,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的政府想找漏洞总能找到 你呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}our government always finds a loophole. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 一样\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,运动队和俱乐部能夺回他们在年鉴中的版面吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can sports and clubs get their pages back in the yearbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 停车吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, stop the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 别说话 Shawn\N{\fnArial\fs18}- What? - Quiet, Shawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛呀? 你俩处得多好呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why? You two are getting along great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就凭Robert一个劲叫我Darcy\N{\fnArial\fs18}I should've known this wasn't a real date
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,该知道这不是什么约会\N{\fnArial\fs18}when Robert here kept calling me "Darcy."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 女士\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还叫"女士"\N{\fnArial\fs18}And "ma'am."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你想靠一场所谓的约会买我口软吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You were trying to buy my influence with a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,美国人不都是这么干的 小伙伴\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's how we do it in America, comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮\N{\fnArial\fs18}Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 别说话 Shawn\N{\fnArial\fs18}- What? - Quiet, Shawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,卡片顺序乱了\N{\fnArial\fs18}The cards got mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在开始 你吃午餐要另寻好桌了\N{\fnArial\fs18}From now on, you'll have to find a different table at lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就下周一周\N{\fnArial\fs18}For the next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 谢谢你\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这张太棒了 痛感非常真实\N{\fnArial\fs18}This one's great. You can really feel the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不过蹦床旁边不是应该有监护人的吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But aren't there supposed to be spotters at the trampoline?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得 就算有监护人 她也免不了这一摔了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, I don't think even spotters could've stopped that fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 她没事\N{\fnArial\fs18}Anyway, she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,其实她今天玩高低杠还摔了 所以显然是她自己的问题\N{\fnArial\fs18}In fact, she fell off the uneven bars today, so it was clearly her own fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,暴民们来了\N{\fnArial\fs18}The angry villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要拿回属于自己的年鉴版面\N{\fnArial\fs18}We want our rightful yearbook pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,几个局外人对年鉴的制作方向指手画脚 这不公平\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's not fair that a couple of outsiders are dictating the way yearbook is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 这两位局外人的建议非常中肯\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, these two outsiders made a good suggestion,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,既然非常中肯 谁还管它公不公平\N{\fnArial\fs18}and if it's a good suggestion, who cares if it's fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,坚守阵地 他们休想轰走我们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Stand your ground. They can't make us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 大家伙\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛不等卡仕曼特价促销季过去 我们再来这里摊牌?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why don't we postpone the showdown until after the sale at Cashman's?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没那么快\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不给个说法 我是不会走的\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm not leaving until I get results.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不如我们比握力一决胜负吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Shall we settle it with a grip contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,啥意思?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这书呆子整我\N{\fnArial\fs18}The geek's hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝儿 你还好吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Babe! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 我得去找工会谈谈\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's it. I'm talking to the union.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,明年指导象棋俱乐部\N{\fnArial\fs18}Next year, chess club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,刚那套真厉害\N{\fnArial\fs18}That was a good trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,静力训练\N{\fnArial\fs18}Isometric exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我从十岁起就开始练了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I've been doing them since age ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ted 我在想啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ted, I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能不能打破一下仅限年鉴的规则 去吃点披萨?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can we bend our yearbook-only policy and maybe go out for some pizza?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来蛮不错的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Pizza sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,披萨... 啥意思啊?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Pizza... what's it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不想说 但我得承认挺爱吃这种加工奶酪\N{\fnArial\fs18}I hate to say it, but I think I enjoy this processed cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是怎么加工的啊?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What kind of process do they use?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以当它是无糖版的叮当和火火 (甜食)\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's a sugarless version of the one for Ding-Dongs and Ho-Hos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,叮当和火火\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ding-Dongs and Ho-Hos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你太扯了\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才会比较喜欢你吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}I think that's kind of why I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我也喜欢你\N{\fnArial\fs18}I like you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是最扯的地方\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's what's really crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Barch老师\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ms. Barch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解你要削减俱乐部在年鉴里的照片版面\N{\fnArial\fs18}I understand you're cutting the club pictures out of the yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们打算将重点转移到...\N{\fnArial\fs18}We decided to shift the emphasis...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,省省吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道科学俱乐部的指导老师是谁嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know who the faculty advisor to the Science Club is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个一直赞助...\N{\fnArial\fs18}The same person who sponsors
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,朗岱尔高中"夺回夜幕"女子自卫俱乐部的人\N{\fnArial\fs18}the Take Back the Night Lawndale High School women's self-defense club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 我们这种堕落的局外人吃完披萨都干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, what do degenerate outsiders like us do after pizza?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得可以去游乐场玩点电玩什么的\N{\fnArial\fs18}I thought maybe we could play some video games at the arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,别了吧 我看别了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, no, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,口香糖可以 但...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Gum is one thing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,电玩无害的\N{\fnArial\fs18}They're harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,再说了 就算你想排斥 也要先了解一下才好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Besides, if you're drafted, you need to know about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是有点好奇\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess I am a little curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}好玩先生游戏厅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,走着 伙计们 我们过去\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on, dudes, let's get over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,搅黄那个Darcy小妞和她的男朋友\N{\fnArial\fs18}So we can hassle that chick Darcy and her date.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,想不起来了 不过应该很重要的\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't remember, but I think it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,二位想玩什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,城堡场景 水下宫殿 还是未来地狱?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Castle scenario, underwater paradise, futuristic dystopia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,选城堡吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess the castle one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 老大\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okey-doke, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,太过了 是吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's too much, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我都有点受不了自己了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I feel a little sick myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这里并没如实反映中世纪社会的场景\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's not really representative of medieval society,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我得承认这是我这辈子见过最酷的场景了\N{\fnArial\fs18}but I have to say this is the coolest thing I've ever seen in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这俩人是我们朋友\N{\fnArial\fs18}Uh, those are some friends of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能加入吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can we join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,国王宝座\N{\fnArial\fs18}The royal throne!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 我得坐下歇会儿\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good. I need to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,先别急 怪胎们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not so fast, weirdoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Robert?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,请加我Robert大人 Darcy\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's Sir Robert, Darcy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ted?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ted?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:18:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我自学了十一世纪的舞剑手稿\N{\fnArial\fs18}I taught myself from the eleventh-century manuscript on swordplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,太小菜了\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没门 我不会善罢甘休的 跟上来\N{\fnArial\fs18}No way. I'm not going out like this. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 Daria 我们能追上他们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let's go, Daria. We can catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的有点恶心了 你先去吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is making me nauseous. You go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ted 游戏厅马上就要关门了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ted, they're gonna close up pretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们先拔电源再说\N{\fnArial\fs18}They'll have to pull the plug, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有很多战役 对不 伙计们?\N{\fnArial\fs18}We still have a lot of fight left. Right, men?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,全都怪我自己\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's my own fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他最开始都不想去游戏厅的\N{\fnArial\fs18}He didn't even want to go to the arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉过你\N{\fnArial\fs18}I told you:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次约会 顶多街头涂鸦或者瞎逛\N{\fnArial\fs18}first date, stick to vandalism and loitering,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可怎拦得住你非要与众不同\N{\fnArial\fs18}but you always have to be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抬头\N{\fnArial\fs18}Heads up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做的 就是不要在手腕部位较劲\N{\fnArial\fs18}What you want to do is take the strain off your wrist
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,用上更多肘部的力量\N{\fnArial\fs18}and use more of your elbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样\N{\fnArial\fs18}Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 你得在游戏机上亲自示范下\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, yeah! You gotta show me on the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,放学后怎么样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀 你知不知道哪儿能搞点口香糖来的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay. You don't know where we might obtain some gum, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,男生耍剑\N{\fnArial\fs18}Boys playing swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看来这事儿没看起来那么简单\N{\fnArial\fs18}I think that probably has some significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我们还在为年鉴的事做有意义的斗争\N{\fnArial\fs18}At least we're still fighting the good fight at yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,回头见了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ah, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,关于从运动队和俱乐部要过来的版面 我有点坏消息要说\N{\fnArial\fs18}I have some bad news about those pages we took from sports and clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,女人啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ow, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点事要跟你们说\N{\fnArial\fs18}I have to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你入了邪教了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You joined the cult?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没有邪教\N{\fnArial\fs18}There's no cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我从年鉴组里退出了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I had to resign from yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是出于道义之选\N{\fnArial\fs18}It was a question of ethics.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,又来?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 她怎么也待了一礼拜呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't worry, she was on staff for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可以写进大学申请书里了\N{\fnArial\fs18}She can still put it on her college application!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不想问问道义上的问题吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}No questions about ethics here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那我还能拿到网页软件啥的吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, then, can I keep the web page stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经给Quinn了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Actually, we gave it to Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn? 她已经拆包装了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn? Did she remove the shrink-wrap?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:19:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不信\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,全都你自己做的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You did this yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我在学校认识一个更萌的技术帝 他帮我搞定的\N{\fnArial\fs18}I had one of the cuter technical types from school set it up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,说清楚点\N{\fnArial\fs18}I had to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉你和那个什么Ted没有结果哦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, sorry it didn't work out with that Ted guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是很有趣 我发现他其实还蛮酷蛮有趣的呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Isn't it funny that now it turns out that he's sort of cool and interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 滑稽\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 快来看\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey! Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,过去三小时 都有250人踩过我的主页了\N{\fnArial\fs18}My web page had twenty-five hundred hits in just the last three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛 我能轻易战胜\N{\fnArial\fs18}Really? I can beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你都没有网页的好吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}You don't even have a web page.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是没 但我会踩\N{\fnArial\fs18}No... but I can hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn迷你简汉真广标\fsp1\c&HE6ECE8&\pos(400,156)}欢迎微博关注\N\N{\fs28}@漫迪字幕组
